<title component="metadata">Alineado con <xref ref="lec-areaDeRectangulos" text="title"/></title>

<statement>
  <p>Encuentra el área del rectángulo. Explica o muestra tu razonamiento.</p>
  <image source="svg-source/tikz-file-151453.svg">
    <shortdescription>Diagram. Rectangle partitioned into 5 rows of 8 of the same size squares.</shortdescription>
  </image>
</statement>

<solution>
  <p>[++++++++++++++++++++]</p>
  <p>40 square units. Sample response: Each column has 5 squares, so there are 5, 10, 15, 20, 25, 30, 35, 40 squares total.</p>
</solution>

